                        <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#0F2E2E]" style="">3.5k <span
                                class="text-xs font-medium text-on-surface-variant" style="">este mes</span></p>
                        <div class="mt-2 w-full bg-white rounded-full h-1.5 overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="bg-secondary h-full" style="width: 80%"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-widest mb-4" style="">Eventos
