                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-surface transition-colors border-l-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xs text-on-surface-variant" data-icon="error"
                                style="">error</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-on-surface" style="">Reporte Crítico de Plaga: Gusano
